block content
	.articleContent
		p The digital team is redesigning our online content and building a new case management system for Citizens Advice based on user need.

		p Starting with real user needs and understanding the tasks that people actually need to complete is key to our approach and there are lots of ways you can help.

		h3 If you work in a local Citizens Advice

		p We always need local staff and volunteers to test out our other ideas and prototypes and give us feedback, particularly those from local Citizens Advice we’ve not already worked with.

		p Please email us with your name, role and location and we’ll add you to our mailing list for research and testing.

		p Hundreds of staff and volunteers are already helping us with our research and testing. This map shows all the locations we’ve been working with and where we have gaps:

